    <section id="timeline" class="mb-16" aria-labelledby="timeline-title">
      <h2 id="timeline-title" class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Typical Renovation Timeline</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Planning and Design (2-4 weeks)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Finalize design, materials, budget, and contractor selection.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Permits and Approvals (1-3 weeks)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Submit for permits and wait for approval from local authorities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Demolition and Prep (1-2 weeks)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Remove old materials, prep the space, and address hidden issues.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Rough Work (2-4 weeks)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Electrical, plumbing, HVAC, framing, and insulation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Inspections (1-2 days)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Municipal inspections of electrical, plumbing, and structural work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Finish Work (3-6 weeks)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Drywall, painting, flooring, cabinetry, fixtures, and final details.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-brand-secondary);">
          <h3 class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Final Inspection and Walkthrough (1 week)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Final municipal approval and a detailed walkthrough with the contractor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm mt-6 italic" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        <strong>Total typical timeline:</strong> 10-20 weeks for a comprehensive renovation. Unexpected issues can extend timelines.
      </div>
    </section>

